<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Loan Repayment Reminder</title>
<style>
  .status-overdue {
    color: red;
  }
  .status-upcoming {
    color: #FF6F00;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f6f9fc; padding: 20px;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center; background-color: #FF6F00; border-top-left-radius: 8px; border-top-right-radius: 8px;">
        <h2 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0;">
          <% if (isAfterDueDate) { %>
            Payment Overdue Reminder
          <% } else { %>
            Upcoming Loan Repayment Reminder
          <% } %>
        </h2>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 20px;">
        <p>Dear <strong><%= customerName %></strong>,</p>

        <% if (isAfterDueDate) { %>
          <p>We noticed that your loan repayment due on <strong><%= dueDate %></strong> has not yet been received.</p>
          <p>To avoid late payment charges or negative impact on your credit record, please make the payment at the earliest.</p>
        <% } else { %>
          <p>This is a friendly reminder that your upcoming loan repayment is due on <strong><%= dueDate %></strong>.</p>
          <p>We kindly request you to ensure timely payment to avoid any late fees or impact on your credit record.</p>
        <% } %>

        <table cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;">
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Loan ID:</strong></td>
            <td><%= loanId %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Amount Due:</strong></td>
            <td class="<%= isAfterDueDate ? 'status-overdue' : 'status-upcoming' %>">
              <%= amountDue %>
            </td>
            <td><strong>Due Date:</strong></td>
            <td><%= dueDate %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Status:</strong></td>
            <td class="<%= isAfterDueDate ? 'status-overdue' : 'status-upcoming' %>">
              <%= isAfterDueDate ? 'Overdue' : 'Upcoming' %>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
          <a href="<%= paymentLink %>" style="background-color: #FF6F00; color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">
            <%= isAfterDueDate ? 'Pay Now' : 'Pay in Advance' %>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p>If you have already made the payment, kindly ignore this message.</p>

        <p>For any assistance, feel free to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #FF6F00;"><%= supportEmail %></a>.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for your cooperation.</p>

        <p>Warm regards,<br><strong><%= companyName %></strong> Team</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 15px; background-color: #f1f5f9; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
        © <%= year %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
